			<h2>War makes facists of us all: Would you like to know more?</h2>
			<p class="entry-meta meta-top">
                <span class="entry-date">16 June 2010</span> | 
                David Eaves |  
                <span class="entry-comments"><a href="http://eaves.ca/2010/06/16/war-makes-facists-of-us-all-would-you-like-to-know-more/#respond" title="Comment on War makes facists of us all: Would you like to know more?"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="2665 http://eaves.ca/?p=2665">View Comments</span></a></span>
            </p>
			<div class="entry">
			<!-- begin share & edit block -->
			<div class="meta-share-edit">
				<h3>Share</h3>
